Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去吹吹风…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？ 用我陪你么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家是来帮长野原同学弄原稿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 名乃也真是够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了 已经到这个时间了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这下可不能糊里糊涂的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃回来之前 我们一口气加快进度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟明天是投稿截止日期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有很会画的一面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就给你搞定哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员战斗开始～～！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么快就开始偷懒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么那么 我稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.05,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\move(878,207,887,194)}要\N是\N做\N一\N匹\N太\N过\N的\N烈\N马\N的\N话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.05,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\move(171,318,144,315)}我\N可\N要\N打\N你\N了\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.05,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\move(491,581,478,602,22,2524)}我\N说\N…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可要打你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说麻衣 你画了什么啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空也上人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}空也（903-972）：平安时代中期僧侣，天台宗空也派的祖师。\N人称阿弥陀圣、市圣、市上人等。民间也有评价称其为净土教的先驱者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那个问题哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么擅自画上去了呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为背景的空白在哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说神马！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之快把那里涂上白色！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里只有网点就可以了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它乱七八糟的都是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我这辈子觉得最痛的一次了哦 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈… 赶快给头发上色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那——个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我我我我我我我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个… 诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个… ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画错了的话 或者有什么失误的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之要马上说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之不赶快修正的话！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 完成啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再擅自乱画了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(879,208)}要\N是\N做\N一\N匹\N太\N过\N的\N烈\N马\N的\N话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs33\frz35.158\pos(149,277)}墓\N地\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(479,584)}我\N说\N…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.08,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs48\frz35.158\pos(203,267)\c&H656363&}墓\N地\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓… 地哦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你个笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是代官山的高级宫殿啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说 画上去 是不行的吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么擅自乱画呢！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那里有空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棘手——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 算了… 总之好好给我擦掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只擦掉就够了啊！！ 只擦掉哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画了一个很帅的出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说画了一个很帅的出来了 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像么！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的给她也是火上浇油！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次好好擦掉了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 乱做多余的事 可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(879,208)}要\N是\N做\N一\N匹\N太\N过\N的\N烈\N马\N的\N话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs33\frz35.158\pos(149,277)}墓\N地\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(479,584)}我\N说\N…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我把你擦掉吗！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要擅自做这种事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个漫画不怎么有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把话说的太狠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你一张新的稿纸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那张纸上画上同样的网格线…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有网格线哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs90\c&H000000&\bord0\shad4\4c&HFCFCFC&\frz270\b1\pos(865,300)}Helvitica
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs90\c&H000000&\bord0\shad4\4c&HFCFCFC&\frz270\b1\pos(777,435)}Standard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收…收拾不了——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是像与不像的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 是谁啊！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的给她看也是火上浇油哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…真的只有网格线吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 有一个老爷爷和老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷去上山砍柴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是从桃子里出来的 二号生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣… 你去… 看书吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉越着急就越糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了… 不好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊… 怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你能做到么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能画出来么 麻衣！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能做出…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说… 诶！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个也非常激烈的厉害！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激烈的 越来越远啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧… 回到那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对身边的一切还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么东西都觉得很新鲜的 那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 说出来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将原原本本的自己！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万分抱歉啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您重新画一张！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有稿纸了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 走廊里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笹原！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}只{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}语
加一句“死小鬼”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 拿不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么含义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长野原前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没没没没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me  too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没 倒也… 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明离大赛越来越近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却很难集中精神练习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长野原前辈高中的时候有遇到过这种事么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉防具沉的要命之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没在听…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎茸三昧这本漫画 真是奇怪呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这家伙除了剑道以外都 完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 什么什么？ 有趣的事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长野原前辈你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要参加全日本大赛了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道场也不来 美星她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 本来是要去买东西的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你煎饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么呢 在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才啊 长野原前辈来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？ 明天都是全日本大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？ 明天么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说些什么了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这个丢给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好红呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:26.37,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fad(400,0)}菠\N萝\N包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1\blur2\c&H181818&\frz21.551\move(603,294,602,282)}菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord1\blur2\c&H181818&\frz21.551\move(712,531,722,558)}食用期限在面包的背面标明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HD6A6FE&\pos(622,498)}与爱有关的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 美绪 来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心里想着偶尔也要换一个形象 就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合适么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很小佑风…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.37,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\fscx95\bord2\pos(150,570)}雪\N飘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.37,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs21\bord2\pos(212,570)}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那～ 我来找了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 在哪里啦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生 发～现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侥幸这种东西可真可怕啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种小孩子的游戏 我一般是不掺合的呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 偶尔也要跟你们一起玩玩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快继续哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦诶 小鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底藏哪了啊 这小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话可绝对不会被发现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼的话 可能藏到家外面了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定意外的就这样一辈子都找不到了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是自己做的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不就不是捉迷藏了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我以为你们已经找不到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擤——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擤… 鼻涕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要洗的衣物不是又多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我做鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来玩 下一把吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 博士给你洗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会变得乱糟糟的 还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会变得乱糟糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不 肯定会乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\bord0\shad4\4c&HF4F2F1&\c&H96D291&}P{\c&H06BDE9&}y{\c&H0E009B&}o{\c&H92F052&}n{\c&H6F54E8&}是{\c&H7EA1AD&}这{\c&H7C1EA2&}个{\c&H5D4542&}样{\c&H33FF6C&}子{\2c&H964CAE&\c&H974DAE&}的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 你说了什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你妹啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 来帮我我当然很高兴了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄翻墨水的是小佑你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经没有稿纸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有办法跟小佑你说去买的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 你说什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 到底我们谁去买…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚣张你妹啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把墨水弄翻的小佑你干的你进去买啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有很多事情没做完呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果是该小佑去买东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又说了什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来像几岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁管你啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢进去的话 文具店要关门了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在突然问啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟实际年龄一样啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿鞋的时候你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好冷哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挥泪斩马谡哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要顽抗到什么时候啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天一点也不冷啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那也算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 结果买回来的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你买的是稿纸啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要开这种玩笑了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说完这话 你拿出来的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进退维谷啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你想让我怎样啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我那么说了 你又说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧风信子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风信子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岂止是无聊啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风信子是从哪出来的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那样我也相信你了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信你会好好把稿纸买回来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信那是一个太冷的笑话！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟你说快把稿纸拿出来结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么了！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美绪 把头脑风信子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风信子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该把头脑冷静下来的是谁啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}译注：风信子{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（ヒヤシンス）{\r\fs36}和冷静{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（ひやす）{\r\fs36}音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不是不是 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁该风信子啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我又问了一遍啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问你“实际上是买了吧”！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果 你说什么了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风信子哪去了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说 风信子怎么着都随便啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稿纸啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果 你拿出来的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对对对 这个这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 用淫靡的文笔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来写一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个蠢货！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要前言不答后语到什么程度才肯罢休啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底想要干什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实不一定是总是正确的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小佑办不成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拜托名乃去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她说去买稿纸什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入迷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛像被钉住了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是喜极而泣啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法所以拜托麻衣去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 可以帮我去买么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\bord0\shad0\c&H455D66&\frz31.216\pos(740,424)\frx44\fry14}我\N回\N去\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声都没吱就回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样都按麻衣的步调来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣的步调 就是我行我素啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}译注：麻衣的步调{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（まいのペース）{\r\fs30}与我行我素{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（マイペース）{\r\fs30}音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 看着那个纸条的小佑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得你说什么了么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是神的恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是恶魔的 陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的陷阱啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从你们几个来的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已经是恶魔的陷阱了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了那些后 小佑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想听你的解释呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个 超级大傻瓜！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是不是 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说还是花生米都没有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花生米混蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直说“就是说”“就是说”什么的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅你了 风信子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:06.89,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\blur3}あの素晴らしい愛をもう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:06.89,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\blur3}让那何等美妙的爱情再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:29.21,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命かけてと　誓った日から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:29.21,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}从立下赌上生命 的誓言的那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:38.76,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}素敵な思い出　残してきたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:38.76,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}明明还留下 那绝佳的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:47.73,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あの時　同じ花を見て　美しいと言った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:47.73,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}那个时候 看到同一朵花 都会说好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:58.94,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ふたりの　心と心が　今はもう通わない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:58.94,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如今我二人 心与心之间 竟无法相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:08.25,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あの素晴らしい愛をもう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:08.25,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让那何等美妙的爱情再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:20.72,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)\blur3}あの素晴らしい愛をもう一度

Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:20.72,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)\blur3}让那何等美妙的爱情再一次

Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是助你走向梦想的摆渡人 漫画稿纸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛 堂堂正正的朝着描绘梦想的海报发射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一话日常是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有送上门来的哦！